    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >二次元高机动FPS<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353050/extras/5e2ce26bc3227fd1bbd10578048be6d6.poster.avif?t=1770292470\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353050/extras/5e2ce26bc3227fd1bbd10578048be6d6.webm?t=1770292470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353050/extras/5e2ce26bc3227fd1bbd10578048be6d6.mp4?t=1770292470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WTF</strong> 是一款二次元风格的第一人称战术竞技射击游戏。<strong>WTF</strong> 回归多人FPS的本质：在专为高机动性和垂直立体作战设计的小型地图上，展开激烈的阵地战和狂热的交火。冲突随着每一回合不断升级。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >深度自定义<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353050/extras/1fd8bc006ecf925d21408cb996e3d122.poster.avif?t=1770292470\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353050/extras/1fd8bc006ecf925d21408cb996e3d122.webm?t=1770292470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353050/extras/1fd8bc006ecf925d21408cb996e3d122.mp4?t=1770292470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >赢得比赛获取资源来建设你的 <strong>母基地</strong>，从而解锁更多带入战场的枪械、专长、技能和皮肤。通过深度的装备与专长定制，钻研并打造完美的配装。每一回合都面临新的升级决策，这将决定你的胜利之路。每局选择新专长，构筑你的终极形态。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不萌即死<strong>(づ•̀⩊•)づ︻╦̵̵̿╤──</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353050/extras/cadb16fde8e40d1472de2f52e24f9039.poster.avif?t=1770292470\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353050/extras/cadb16fde8e40d1472de2f52e24f9039.webm?t=1770292470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353050/extras/cadb16fde8e40d1472de2f52e24f9039.mp4?t=1770292470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3A级网络代码</strong>配备区域专用服务器。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>针对低配设备优化</strong>流畅运行 60+ FPS。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>拒绝臃肿</strong>的“长期服务”内容。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >组建终极“老婆”军团</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353050/extras/96d31d37a7b62ecbcd1e526f4e1b4e1c.poster.avif?t=1770292470\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353050/extras/96d31d37a7b62ecbcd1e526f4e1b4e1c.webm?t=1770292470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353050/extras/96d31d37a7b62ecbcd1e526f4e1b4e1c.mp4?t=1770292470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用比赛奖金资助你的佣兵公司。解锁并招募新干员助战，扩建你的 <strong>母基地</strong>。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战斗中赢取基地和公司升级。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级 <strong>母基地</strong> 以解锁新专长武器和角色。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与其他玩家合作，或入侵他们的 <strong>母基地</strong>，实现世界征服。</p></li></ul>",
